Login:
POST /login

Body:

{
  "username": "username",
  "password": "password"
}
Upload File:
POST /upload-file

Body:

multipart/form-data

file: (file to upload)
Sign Up:
POST /sign-up

Body:

{
  "email": "email@example.com",
  "password": "password"
}
Email Verify:
GET /email-verify?encrypted_url={{encrypted_url}}
Download File:
GET /download-file/{{file_id}}
List All Uploaded Files:
GET /list-all-uploaded-files
Example Postman requests:

// Login
POST http://localhost:8000/login

Body:

```json
{
  "username": "username",
  "password": "password"
}

// Upload File
POST http://localhost:8000/upload-file

Body:

multipart/form-data

file: (file to upload)

// Sign Up
POST http://localhost:8000/sign-up

Body:

```json
{
  "email": "email@example.com",
  "password": "password"
}
